---
title: Thai Spiced Stargazer with Black Rice, Bok Choy and Coconut
description: We love the firm, meaty texture of stargazer. It's very similar to monkfish so can hold its own against some strong spicing and is perfect in this Thai-influenced dish. The fragrant fish is served with black rice, bok choy and a zingy coriander dressing. All finished with coconut, this exotic feast is as dramatic to look at as it is to eat!
